Class EJBProducer

java.lang.Object
  com.armandorv.cnpd.web.server.ejb.EJBProducer

@ApplicationScoped
public class EJBProducer
extends java.lang.Object

Factory that produces instances to work against the EJB facades of business tier. This factory is used by CDI container to inject EJB proxies into web tier CDI contextual instances.
